      "effects": [],
      "system": {
        "subType": "spell",
        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 6 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 60&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>May be used in one of two situations:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Battle:</strong> Allies within a 20&rsquo; square area who are not yet in melee gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls and a +1 bonus to morale.</li>\n<li><strong>Ritual:</strong> Casting bless may also form part of rituals of purification or consecration, at the referee&rsquo;s discretion.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Reversed: Blight</strong></p>\n<p>Incurs a &ndash;1 penalty to morale checks, attack rolls, and damage rolls of enemies within a 20&rsquo; square area. A save versus spells is allowed to resist the blight.</p>",
