      "effects": [],
      "system": {
        "subType": "spell",
        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 12 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 10&rsquo; around the caster</strong></p>\n<p>This spell wards the caster and all allies within 10&rsquo; from attacks by creatures of another alignment, as follows:</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Bonuses:</strong> Those warded gain a +1 bonus to saving throws against attacks or special abilities of affected creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Affected creatures&rsquo; attacks: </strong>Against those warded are penalised by &ndash;1.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Enchanted, constructed, or summoned </strong><strong>creatures: </strong>The spell additionally prevents such creatures from making melee attacks against those warded, though they may still make ranged attacks. If any of the warded party engages such a creature in melee, this protection is broken (those warded still gain the save and attack bonuses mentioned above).</p>",
