        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 9 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 180&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>This spell causes one or more humans, demihumans, or human-like monsters to be paralysed if they fail a Mental save. It may be cast in two ways:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Against an individual:</strong> The target&rsquo;s saving throw is penalised by &ndash;2.</li>\n<li><strong>Against a group:</strong> 1d4 individuals in the group are targeted.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Restrictions:</strong> Human-like monsters of greater than 4+1 HD and undead are not affected.</p>",
