        }
      },
      "effects": [],
      "system": {
        "subType": "spell",
        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: 12 turns</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 180&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>A 15&rsquo; radius area is rendered utterly silent.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Within the area:</strong> All sound is stopped. Conversation and spell casting are impossible.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Noise from outside the area:</strong> Can be heard by those within it.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Casting upon a creature: </strong>Silence may be cast upon a creature, which must make a Mental save. If the save fails, the 15&rsquo; radius area of silence moves with the creature. If the save succeeds, the spell&rsquo;s effect remains stationary&mdash;the targeted creature may move out of it.</p>",
